description:
This is a 12 minute workout called 'Morning Shred Routine - Burn Belly Fat' from the channel Adam Frater.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: In this video I show you my favorite morning home workout routine to get you shredded. If you want to lose weight, get stronger and finally build that 6 pack in 2022 this one is perfect for you. If you're looking for more workouts and calisthenics/home based workouts make sure to subscribe to my channel. Enjoy!
